      6.
EDDIE
(into his headset)
Cue 453, go.
Shelly, Mary-Anne and Jodie jazz rush into the blinding 
lights on the stage.
TITLE CARD: THE LAST SHOWGIRL
INT. SUPERMARKET - DAY.
Shelly and her best friend ANNETTE (60, amazing legs, ex￾showgirl) are at the checkout counter.
INT. SUPERMARKET. SELF CHECK-OUT - MOMENTS LATER
Shelly tries to scan her items as Annette flips through 
People Magazine. 
ANNETTE
So who’s the guy? 
SHELLY
Rick. He saw me leaving the 
theater.
ANNETTE
Ooh a little stage door Johnny 
situation? Paging stage door 
Johnnayyy!! Aisle four!
SHELLY
No, shh! No-- he recognized me in 
the parking lot.
ANNETTE
He think you’re an escort on the 
side?
SHELLY
No, Annette.
ANNETTE
Guys think that! Well they do.
SHELLY
Rick is nice. He likes me. He 
doesn’t think that.
CHECK OUT MACHINE
Please scan your item again.
