      66.
JODIE
What did you do??
SHELLY
(emotional again)
I ripped it up.
Jodie puts her hands on Shelly and Mary-Anne’s knees.
SHELLY (CONT'D)
I had this dream the other night 
that I could speak French... I was 
really-- I was speaking French. 
Really speaking it. And I-- I 
understood everything...
JODIE
You should go to France.
